                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8860" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1351</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2193 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">与消费者共生：安踏集团的数字营销实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Symbiosis with Consumers: Anta Group&#39;s Digital Marketing Practice</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王永贵，王冬雪，马双，汪淋淋，姚鹏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安踏体育用品集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安踏集团；与消费者共生；数字营销；价值共创；品牌沟通；2024百优案例；重点项目；系列8-7</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ANTA; Symbiosis with consumers; Digital marketing; Value co-creation; Brand Communication</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着越来越多的运动品牌在行业崭露头角，安踏集团面临着愈发激烈的竞争压力。作为行业领跑者，安踏始终坚守“将超越自我的体育精神融入每个人的生活”的企业使命，在新的发展阶段提出“与消费者共生”理念，从一众品牌中脱颖而出。顺应数字转型和低碳发展的时代潮流，安踏在数字技术的赋能下持续深耕运动用品行业，积极探索与消费者的共创共生共赢之路。在“与消费者共生”的理念引领下，安踏在产品开发、渠道运营和品牌传播的各个环节运用数字技术与消费者建立紧密联结，通过专业、环保的产品品质、企业服务和品牌理念调动顾客参与价值共创活动的积极性，在双向互动中打造互利共赢的合作关系，实现安踏与消费者的共同成长。通过对本案例的学习和讨论，能够帮助学员深刻理解新的商业环境下企业与消费者的互利共生关系，掌握以数字营销实现价值共创的实践内容和背后逻辑，从而为企业运用数字技术建立起与消费者的紧密联系提供借鉴和参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As more and more sports brands emerge in the industry, Anta Group is facing increasingly fierce competitive pressure. As a leader in the industry, Anta has always adhered to the corporate mission of &quot;integrating the sportsmanship beyond itself into everyone&#39;s life&quot;, and put forward the concept of &quot;symbiosis with consumers&quot; in the new stage of development, standing out from all brands. In line with the trend of the times of digital transformation and low-carbon development, Anta continues to deepen the sporting goods industry under the empowerment of digital technology, and actively explores the road of co-creation, symbiosis and win-win with consumers. Under the guidance of the concept of &quot;symbiosis with consumers&quot;, Anta uses digital technology to establish a close connection with consumers in all aspects of product development, channel operation and brand communication, and mobilizes customers through professional and environmentally friendly product quality, corporate services and brand concepts Participate in the enthusiasm of value co-creation activities, create a mutually beneficial and win-win cooperative relationship in two-way interaction, and realize the common growth of Anta and consumers. Through the study and discussion of this case, it can help students deeply understand the mutually beneficial symbiotic relationship between enterprises and consumers in the new business environment, and master the practical content and logic behind the realization of value co-creation through digital marketing, so as to establish for enterprises to use digital technology Provide reference and reference for establishing a close connection with consumers.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《品牌管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌沟通；数字营销；数字化客户关系管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
